SubtitleSequenceText.SourceString: Your kingdom was at peace, when without warning, monsters from space attacked.
SubtitleSequenceText.LocalizedString: Your kingdom was at peace, when without warning, monsters from space attacked.

SubtitleSequenceText.SourceString: Smashing deep into the ground, they trapped the world and its heroes in techno-magic crystal.
SubtitleSequenceText.LocalizedString: Smashing deep into the ground, they trapped the world and its heroes in techno-magic crystal.

SubtitleSequenceText.SourceString: Now it's up to you to assemble the ultimate team of super warriors, and take back your planet, one break at a time.
SubtitleSequenceText.LocalizedString: Now it's up to you to assemble the ultimate team of super warriors, and take back your planet, one break at a time.

SubtitleSequenceText.SourceString: ♪ Monsters from the sky want us all to die ♪
SubtitleSequenceText.LocalizedString: ♪ Monsters from the sky want us all to die ♪

SubtitleSequenceText.SourceString: ♪ They're hiding under ground, now they all must be found ♪
SubtitleSequenceText.LocalizedString: ♪ They're hiding under ground, now they all must be found ♪

SubtitleSequenceText.SourceString: ♪ Break the crystals, set them free ♪
SubtitleSequenceText.LocalizedString: ♪ Break the crystals, set them free ♪
